<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271471>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Speodromia platyarthrodes, male (28.1 × 22.1 mm) (SAM MB-A 000816), South Africa. A, left lateral side of cephalothorax; B, right lateral side of cephalothorax (denuded); C, left side of sub-branchial surface showing cavity; D, left side of sub-branchial cavity showing groove towards posterior carapace margin (denuded); E, F, posterior view of cephalothorax." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271471/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

